ğŸ§  Why This Works

â€¢ Prevents `NoneType` errors by validating agent existence
â€¢ Ensures every agent returned is a subclass of `BaseAgent`
â€¢ Logs instantiation success and failure clearly
â€¢ Supports both positional dependency injection and optional config


